  <entry>
    <title>算法</title>
    <url>/2023/10/10/algorithm/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>牛顿勘根法<br>原理：1.选择一个初始猜测值（通常选择目标平方根的近似值）。<br>2.使用以下公式计算下一个近似值：<br>3.新的近似值 = （当前近似值 + 目标值 / 当前近似值） / 2<br>重复步骤2，直到新的近似值和当前近似值的差小于所需精度。<br><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">sqrt</span>(<span class="params">n</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    approx = n/<span class="number">2.0</span></span><br><span class="line">    better = (approx + n/approx)/<span class="number">2.0</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> better != approx:</span><br><span class="line">        approx = better</span><br><span class="line">        better = (approx + n/approx)/<span class="number">2.0</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> approx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>欧几里得求最大公因数<br>原理：a,b最大公约数(Greatest Common Divisor)，就等于b,a%b的最大公约数.<br><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">gcd</span>(<span class="params">x, y</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> y:</span><br><span class="line">        t = x % y</span><br><span class="line">        x = y</span><br><span class="line">        y = t </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> x</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(gcd(<span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">6</span>))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
]]></content>
